{"tid":2057279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長實趙國雄：國安法立法後香港前景將更明朗 對樓市影響一定正面","createTime":"2020-06-09T09:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T10:38:36.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca424617102e4d0692fcbfb25ac3815c0e5bc038","tid":2057279,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2665000/2665518/SEA03_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2665000%2F2665518%2FSEA03_1024.jpeg&h=2ac84c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政經環境未明朗，本港後市亦因而有所波動。長實執行董事趙國雄指，港區國安法詳情未落實，但個人認為立法是必須的，形容「社會安定，大家置業先安心」。他認為立法後香港前景將更明朗，對樓市影響一定是正面的。<br />\n<br />\n至於立法引起走資及移民潮，趙氏指當然部分人會選擇移民，但移民不代表要賣樓，故對樓市影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n趙國雄預計，下半年經濟料平穩向上，主要因政府於應對新冠肺炎疫情有力，加上一系列保就業措施，料經濟將回穩；至於樓市方面，要視乎個別地區及樓盤，「開價太高銷售有困難」，指集團旗下新盤一向以市價推售，首批更有所折讓，對銷情有信心。<br />\n<br />\n記者：梁可昕<br />\n責任編輯：梁子謙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2665518?fbclid=IwAR2JMEIs0go2uWzhd5hLR861KiJGUbEXFjhAZjB3HVoi6ICzEUfUtNdgSt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2665518%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2JMEIs0go2uWzhd5hLR861KiJGUbEXFjhAZjB3HVoi6ICzEUfUtNdgSt4&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelolS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=108e326f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2665518?fbclid=IwAR2JMEIs0go2uWzhd5hLR861KiJGUbEXFjhAZjB3HVoi6ICzEUfUtNdgSt4</a>"},{"pid":"b8b6ba28a38c0e50018351a762400d0466b2801c","tid":2057279,"uid":32836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"用錢攬撚住實平穩向上<br />\n唔好俾外國勢做鳩到9你<br />\n到時bin撚到你落地獄都唔掂"},{"pid":"eb1e406de5603499aa9b6567ffb97d8c3badd39b","tid":2057279,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"正呀喂，咁投地記得落重d本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11423dd3ff2f76abd2aa3401b500aafe7970